{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"21eb615d47","title":"关于转载上海工商界批评高方的报道的批语","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"82f8cdc17c","index":0,"year":1957,"month":9,"day":25,"articleId":"21eb615d47"}],"tags":[{"id":"9bc2c334c7","name":"批示","type":"文稿类型"},{"id":"dd2b275f6c","name":"毛泽东","type":"人物"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"maoquanji38","name":"毛泽东全集第38卷","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"pdf","author":"张迪杰","files":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/banned-historical-archives/banned-historical-archives0/main/mao-quanji/38-OCR.pdf"}],"authors":[{"id":"261e5467ec","name":"毛泽东"}]},"publication_details":{"maoquanji38":{"comments":[{"id":"7fd331be23","publicationId":"maoquanji38","articleId":"21eb615d47","index":1,"part_index":-99,"offset":-99,"text":"指1957年9月22日《新民报》晚刊刊登的《摆事实，讲道理，比过去，看现在——工商界舌战右派高方》的报道。1957年9月29日，《人民日报》作了转载，题为《这次辩论进行得好——介绍上海工商界对右派分子高方的说理斗争》。高方，当时任上海统益纱广总管理处副总经理。"},{"id":"b13e816ef3","publicationId":"maoquanji38","articleId":"21eb615d47","index":2,"part_index":-99,"offset":-99,"text":"乔木，即胡乔木，当时任中共中央书记处候补书记、毛泽东的秘书。冷西，即吴冷西，当时任新华通讯社社长、《人民日报》总编辑。"}],"contents":[{"id":"06c3d3c765","type":"title","text":"关于转载上海工商界批评高方的报道的批语","index":0,"publicationId":"maoquanji38","articleId":"21eb615d47"},{"id":"7fd331be23","type":"paragraph","text":"乔末、冷西回同志：","index":1,"publicationId":"maoquanji38","articleId":"21eb615d47"},{"id":"b13e816ef3","type":"paragraph","text":"批评高方，写得很好，请转载在人民日报上。以后请鼓励这样有充分说服力的批评。现在的批评中，有很天一部分缺芝充分的说服力，提倡浮夸，很不切实。右派浮夸，左派不应当浮夸","index":2,"publicationId":"maoquanji38","articleId":"21eb615d47"},{"id":"5255e71d5f","type":"paragraph","text":"毛泽东","index":3,"publicationId":"maoquanji38","articleId":"21eb615d47"},{"id":"e142888b0d","type":"paragraph","text":"九月廿五日","index":4,"publicationId":"maoquanji38","articleId":"21eb615d47"}],"page":{"id":"7685071b79","publicationId":"maoquanji38","articleId":"21eb615d47","start":234,"end":234}}}},"__N_SSG":true}